Serverless Instructions for AWS:

1. npm install -g serverless

2. Create Directory structure for application.

For nodejs application:

serverless create --template aws-nodejs --path myService

For python application:

serverless create --template aws-python --path myService

3. Deploy:

cd myService

serverless deploy

REFER: https://serverless.com/framework/docs/providers/aws/examples/hello-world/
